      <prefercite id="aspace_e183be6c06597a5feee89db2bcfe7beb">
         <head>Preferred Citation</head>
         <p>Paul H. Silverstone, Class of 1953, Yale College, Postcard Collection Documenting Yale University (RU 946). Manuscripts and Archives, Yale University Library.</p>  
      </prefercite>
      <arrangement id="aspace_662f3dca26f7c16413a1ad614193734e">
         <head>Arrangement</head>
         <p>The rmaterials are arranged by accession, thereunder alphabetically by publisher.</p>  
      </arrangement>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_c9a7793996c8c6013f2a45b6999fb755">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The materials consists of souvenir postcards of Yale, most of which depict buildings and grounds. Also included are postcards depicting Yale athletics, symbols, and student life.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
